file.content: IF (Vol._Type=="CV"AND(Currency=="USD"OR Currency=="EUR"OR Currency=="GBP")) THEN IR_Vega := Normal_vega ELSE IF (Vol._Type=="SV"AND (Currency=="USD"OR Currency=="EUR"OR Currency=="GBP"OR Currency=="AUD")) THEN IR_Vega := Normal_vega ELSE IF (TYPOLOGY=="Bond Future Option" AND Vol._Type=="") THEN IR_Vega := Bond_vega ELSE IF (TYPOLOGY=="Bond Future Option" AND Vol._Type=="SE") THEN IR_Vega := 0 ELSE IR_Vega := Vega_Yield;
